  "title": "Driver",
  "description": "<h3><strong>🚗</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>Driver (Full-Time)</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Kaki Bukit</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re looking for a <strong>reliable and responsible driver</strong> to join our Awesomedia team!</p>\n<p>Your main duty will be to <strong>send and pick up workers island-wide</strong> to and from job sites.</p>\n<p>You will also assist in <strong>general work and ad-hoc tasks</strong> when required.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive company vehicle to transport workers safely to job sites across Singapore</li>\n  <li>Ensure punctual pick-up and drop-off of workers</li>\n  <li>Assist with loading/unloading materials when needed</li>\n  <li>Support general site and warehouse work as assigned</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and good condition of the company vehicle</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess valid Singapore Class 3 driving licence</li>\n  <li>Familiar with Singapore roads</li>\n  <li>Punctual, responsible, and safety-conscious</li>\n  <li>Able to work flexible hours (including early mornings or evenings when needed)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>To apply:</strong></p>\n<p>📧 Send your details to <a href=\"mailto:jobs@awesomedia.sg\">jobs@awesomedia.sg</a></p>",
